          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bagian "How It Works" -->
    <section id="how-it-works" class="section-padding bg-silver-light">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600/10 border border-blue-600/20 rounded-full text-blue-600 font-semibold text-sm mb-6">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
            Proses Kerja Kami
          </div>
          <h2 class="heading-lg text-charcoal mb-8">Proses Laser Cutting Terstruktur</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-graphite max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Dari konsultasi hingga pengiriman, kami memastikan setiap langkah dilakukan dengan presisi dan transparansi untuk hasil terbaik.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Connector Line -->
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-0.5 bg-silver-mid hidden md:block"></div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 relative">
            <!-- Step 1: Konsultasi -->
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg border-4 border-silver-light z-10 mb-4">
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">1</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Konsultasi & Desain</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">Diskusikan kebutuhan project Anda dan finalisasi desain bersama tim ahli kami.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Step 2: Quote -->
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg border-4 border-silver-light z-10 mb-4">
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">2</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Penawaran Harga</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">Kami memberikan penawaran harga yang transparan dan kompetitif.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Step 3: Produksi -->
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg border-4 border-silver-light z-10 mb-4">
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">3</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Produksi Presisi</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">Proses cutting menggunakan mesin laser fiber tercanggih untuk hasil akurat.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Step 4: Quality Control -->
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg border-4 border-silver-light z-10 mb-4">
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">4</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Quality Control</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">Setiap hasil produksi melewati tahap QC ketat untuk memastikan sesuai spesifikasi.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Step 5: Pengiriman -->
            <div class="text-center flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg border-4 border-silver-light z-10 mb-4">
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">5</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Pengiriman Cepat</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">Pengiriman aman dan tepat waktu ke seluruh area Jabodetabek.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bagian USP -->
    <section id="usp" class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-laser-green/10 border border-laser-green/20 rounded-full text-laser-green font-semibold text-sm mb-6">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            Keunggulan Kami
          </div>
          <h2 class="heading-lg text-charcoal mb-8">Mengapa Memilih Jasa Kami?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-graphite max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Kami tidak hanya menawarkan jasa, kami memberikan jaminan kualitas, kecepatan, dan teknologi terdepan untuk setiap project Anda.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- USP 1: Teknologi -->
          <div class="bg-silver-light p-8 rounded-2xl text-center shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">Teknologi Fiber 12kW</h3>
            <p class="text-graphite text-sm">Satu-satunya penyedia jasa dengan laser fiber 12kW di Jabodetabek, menjamin kecepatan dan presisi cutting metal hingga 20mm.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- USP 2: Garansi -->
          <div class="bg-silver-light p-8 rounded-2xl text-center shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">Garansi Kualitas</h3>
            <p class="text-graphite text-sm">Kami memberikan garansi hasil cutting ulang GRATIS jika hasil tidak sesuai dengan spesifikasi yang disepakati.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- USP 3: Pengiriman -->
          <div class="bg-silver-light p-8 rounded-2xl text-center shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-3">Pengiriman Same-Day</h3>
            <p class="text-graphite text-sm">Layanan pengiriman di hari yang sama tersedia untuk area Jakarta dan Tangerang (syarat & ketentuan berlaku).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Bagian Material -->
    <section id="materials" class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-charcoal/10 border border-charcoal/20 rounded-full text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm mb-6">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
            </svg>
            Material Premium
          </div>
          <h2 class="heading-lg text-charcoal mb-8">Material Pilihan Terbaik</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-graphite max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Kami memproses berbagai jenis material kualitas premium dengan hasil cutting yang presisi dan rapi.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          {MATERIALS.slice(0, 6).map((material, index) => (
            <div class="group bg-silver-light rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 border border-silver-mid/50">
              <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
                <img
                  src={material.image}
                  alt={`Jasa laser cutting material ${material.name}`}
                  class="w-full h-52 object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="400"
                  height="208"
                />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-charcoal/50 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-laser-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="p-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-3 group-hover:text-laser-green transition-colors duration-300">
                  {material.name}
                </h3>
                <p class="text-graphite mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                  {material.description}
                </p>
                
                <!-- Thickness Info -->
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6 p-3 bg-white rounded-lg border border-silver-mid/50">
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-graphite">Ketebalan:</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">{material.thickness}</span>
                </div>
                
                <a href={`/${material.slug}/`} 
                   class="group/link inline-flex items-center font-semibold text-charcoal hover:text-laser-green transition-all duration-300">
